er, every match is a new adventure.\n\nJoin the chaos, embrace the madness, and let's make gorilla tag fun again in Project Ozzy! It\u2019s not just a game, it\u2019s a movement! Monke Luther King would be proud.\n\n--- ", "short_description": "\"Lets Make Gorilla Tag Great Again\" Monke Luther King"}]}, "developer_name": "Ozzy Da Shark", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/projectozzy/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ozzy Da Shark", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/projectozzy/home", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "7800484826687719"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "312600801844182"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "312600801844182"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1721763293, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "312600801844182"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7825205107549024", "version": "6"}, "id": "1211727849743712", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7800484816687720", "is_conc